hopobject.body: real beauty page gbyuksupplements.co.uk “The immediate consequence of a censure motion would be to force Rajoy to explain himself to parliament. This is something he continues to deny. That’s the first advantage of any censure motion; the PM must explain himself. The second would be to see what the alternative to Rajoy would be, and that alternative could come from the opposition, although it is unlikely they could muster enough votes. Or the alternative could come from within the Popular party, which could nominate his replacement.”
